roles.title: Software Engineer
roles.description: Developed and maintained web applications using JavaScript, React, and Node.js. Collaborated with cross-functional teams to define project requirements and deliver high-quality software solutions.

roles.title: Data Analyst
roles.description: Analyzed large datasets to extract actionable insights, improved reporting processes, and presented findings to stakeholders using data visualization tools like Tableau.

roles.title: Marketing Specialist
roles.description: Developed and executed marketing campaigns, managed social media accounts, and collaborated with design teams to create promotional materials that increased brand awareness.

roles.title: Operations Coordinator
roles.description: Coordinated logistics operations, optimized supply chain processes, and ensured timely delivery of goods. Worked closely with vendors and clients to improve service efficiency.
